data.description: Wow is the only way to describe this North Livonia Colonial located on a quiet street within walking distance to parks, schools and Henry Ford field. Updates & features as follows; New vinyl siding and insulation in 2020, decks and sprinklers in 2020, furnace 2021, central air 2018, high quality Anderson replacement windows 2022, hot water tank 2023, stainless kitchen appliances to stay 2020, beautiful  2 year old cabana w/ electricity and ceiling fan 2022. Beautifully updated kitchen with Colonial white raised panel cabinets, granite counters. Original hardwood floors throughout second floor and part of main floor. Large yard with deck, patio. This beauty has it all and won't last long, located close to express ways and shopping. Showings start Saturday morning, Open house 1-4 Sunday 4/28/24
